-- Lehman rebounds, erases early loss
-- 
-- Wed Sep 10, 2008 8:48am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/10/us-markets-stocks-lehman-bell-idUSN1037577520080910

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Lehman Brothers' LEH.N shares rose on Wednesday in volatile trade, erasing earlier losses tied to the company posting a quarterly loss and slashing its annual dividend.  

 Shares in the U.S. No. 4 investment bank were last at $8.74 in pre-market trading on the New York Stock Exchange, up 12 percent from Tuesday's close. (Reporting by  Richard Leong ; Editing by  James Dalgleish )